Ask HN: Best content about energy, electromagnetism, circuits?
text:
I've experienced a sudden interest in physics a few times in my life. Right now is one of those times, I am humbled by the simplicity, elegance, and mystery of the Cosmos. I feel like a little kid right now wanting to ask WHY to everything right now.

If you know any good articles, blogs, sites, podcasts, documentaries, anything really, please share. I am very into this subject right now.

This thread will probably help countless others too are on this same wavelength, same train of thought. :)

Show HN: ChatGPT plugin that summarizes web pages
text:
Hi! We've built a plugin for Chrome that converts web pages to markdown documents and feeds them into ChatGPT for queries. This way you can run prompts on top of web pages, such as:

* Display ChatGPT answers next to search results * Summarise web pages into emails / tweets / articles * Extract data / prices / SEO keywords from web pages * Generate content and email responses with ChatGPT
